Add AverMedia AverTV Satellite Hybrid+FM (A706) card to saa7134 driver.
Working: analog inputs, TV, FM radio and IR remote control.
Untested: DVB-S.

Signed-off-by: Ondrej Zary <linux@rainbow-software.org>
